{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T07:29:21.301934", "event": "LLM_METRIC", "data": {"provider": "google", "model": "gemini-2.5-flash", "prompt_tokens": 760, "completion_tokens": 10, "total_tokens": 854, "latency_ms": 1710, "cost_estimate": 0.00854}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T07:29:21.302280", "event": "AGENT_STEP", "data": {"step": 2, "llm_output": "Action: get_lab_objective(2)"}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T07:29:21.302487", "event": "AGENT_OBSERVATION", "data": {"step": 2, "tool": "get_lab_objective", "args": "2", "observation": "B\u00e0i th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh 2 - GH\u00c9P N\u1ed0I N\u1ed0I TI\u1ebeP (I2C, SPI)\nM\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch:\n- X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ea1ch gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecdc RFID, IC th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh OLED \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda.\n- T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chu\u1ea9n giao ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp I2C, SPI; c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 giao ti\u1ebfp 1 master - nhi\u1ec1u slave tr\u00ean bus I2C.\n- L\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i DS1307 (th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c), OLED SH1106 (hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb), RC522 (\u0111\u1ecdc th\u1ebb RFID 13.56 MHz).\n- X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng \u0111\u00f3ng/m\u1edf c\u1eeda d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o m\u00e3 th\u1ebb RFID v\u00e0 ghi nh\u1eadt k\u00fd \u0111\u00f3ng/m\u1edf c\u1eeda."}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T07:29:23.877374", "event": "LLM_METRIC", "data": {"provider": "google", "model": "gemini-2.5-flash", "prompt_tokens": 938, "completion_tokens": 288, "total_tokens": 1294, "latency_ms": 2574, "cost_estimate": 0.01294}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T07:29:23.877791", "event": "AGENT_STEP", "data": {"step": 3, "llm_output": "Final Answer: \u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Lab 2, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee9ng sau: B\u1ed9 kit STM32F429I, Module Tiny RTC (DS1307 + AT24C32), M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh OLED SH1106 1.3 inch, Module RFID RC522 v\u00e0 th\u1ebb RFID 13.56 MHz. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n STM32CubeIDE v\u00e0 Hercules. C\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft bao g\u1ed3m Datasheet DS1307, AT24C32 v\u00e0 m\u00e3 ngu\u1ed3n th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n sh1106.*, fonts.*, tm_stm32f4_mfrc522.*.\n\nM\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a Lab 2 l\u00e0:\n- X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ea1ch gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecdc RFID, IC th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh OLED \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda.\n- T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chu\u1ea9n giao ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp I2C, SPI; c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 giao ti\u1ebfp 1 master - nhi\u1ec1u slave tr\u00ean bus I2C.\n- L\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i DS1307 (th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c), OLED SH1106 (hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb), RC522 (\u0111\u1ecdc th\u1ebb RFID 13.56 MHz).\n- X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng \u0111\u00f3ng/m\u1edf c\u1eeda d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o m\u00e3 th\u1ebb RFID v\u00e0 ghi nh\u1eadt k\u00fd \u0111\u00f3ng/m\u1edf c\u1eeda."}}
